  "texts": [
    "The chatbot generated 26 valid design brief lists with 140 list items.",
    "The design briefs contained an average of 5.38 list items per discussion (SD = 2.49, min = 3, max = 15).",
    "No relationship was observed between the length of conversations and the number of design brief items.",
    "Accordingly, a more extended discussion did not translate into more ideas and topics for the subsequent generation of design requirements.",
    "Next, to measure the system's performance, we manually analyzed conversation transcripts and corresponding design briefs (see Table 4)."
  ],
